  <md:title>Graphing with Intercepts</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para id="para-00001">By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list id="list-00001">
<item>Identify the intercepts on a graph</item>
<item>Find the intercepts from an equation of a line</item>
