 </row>
 <row>
 <entry>The graph crosses the <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis>-axis at the point (4, 0).</entry>
 <entry>The <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis>-intercept is (4, 0).</entry>
 </row>
 <row>
 <entry>The graph crosses the <emphasis effect="italics">y</emphasis>-axis at the point (0, 2).</entry>
 <entry>The <emphasis effect="italics">y</emphasis>-intercept is (0, 2).</entry>
 </row>
</tbody>




</tgroup>
</table><table id="eip-id1172467254989" class="unnumbered unstyled" summary="."><label/>
<tgroup cols="2"><tbody>
 <row>
 <entry><span class="token">ⓑ</span> </entry>
 <entry/>
 </row>
 <row>
 <entry>The graph crosses the <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis>-axis at the point (2, 0).</entry>
 <entry>The <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis>-intercept is (2, 0)</entry>
 </row>
 <row>
 <entry>The graph crosses the <emphasis effect="italics">y</emphasis>-axis at the point (0, −6).</entry>
