<para id="fs-id1363710">To ensure accuracy, we need to plot three points. Since the intercepts are the same point, we need two more points to graph the line. As always, we can choose any values for <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:math> so we’ll let <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> be <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math> and <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>−1</m:mn><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math><newline/>
