</media>
<para id="fs-id1829837"><span class="token">ⓐ</span> Find the <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mtext>-</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> and <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mtext>-</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> intercepts.</para><para id="fs-id1829855"><span class="token"> ⓑ</span> Explain what the <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mtext>-</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> and <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mtext>-</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> intercepts mean for Ozzie.</para></problem>
